Grant Taylor (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Grant_Taylor_(actor) 0 Grant Taylor (6 December 1917 – 1971), real name Ronald Grant Taylor, was an English-born actor best known as the abrasive General Henderson in the Gerry Anderson science fiction series UFO and for his lead role in Forty Thousand Horsemen (1940).
